<name>2GR-FE ENGINE CONTROL SYSTEM</name>
<ttl id="10006_S000F_7306F_T00E9" variety="T00E9">
<name>ENGINE COOLANT TEMPERATURE SENSOR</name>
<para id="RM0000022NH001X" category="G" type-id="3001K" name-id="ES3PG-02" from="200601">
<name>INSPECTION</name>
<subpara id="RM0000022NH001X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM0000022NH001X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___000092E00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT ENGINE COOLANT TEMPERATURE SENSOR</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Measure the resistance between the terminals.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A092795E03" width="2.775699831in" height="3.779676365in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>Standard resistance</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="2">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="2.07in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="2.06in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Approx. 20°C (68°F)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>2.32 to 2.59 kΩ</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Approx. 80°C (176°F)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>0.31 to 0.326 kΩ</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the result is not as specified, replace the sensor.</ptxt>
<atten3>
<ptxt>If checking the ECT sensor in the water, keep the terminals dry. After checking, dry the sensor.</ptxt>
</atten3>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
